---
import img1 from "../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/oil1.webp";
import LearnBtn from "../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import BurnerVideo from "../../assets/images/Burners/burnerVideo.mp4";
import flag from "../../assets/images/Burners/flag.svg";
import ficha from "../../assets/images/Burners/ficha.png";
import wordIcon from "../../assets/images/Burners/world.png";
import batchIcon from "../../assets/images/Burners/batch.png";
import preHeat from "../../assets/images/Burners/preHeat.png";
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 font-bold">
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full">
    <div
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold w-full text-start max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8"
    >
      <h1 class="text-grisT">BURNERS</h1>
      <div class="mt-4 mb-6 flex">
        <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-red-500"></div>
        <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-gray-300"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 w-full"
    >
      <video src={BurnerVideo} autoplay class="w-1/2"></video>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-center">
        From 6 to 125 million Btu/Hr, with preheater and filter
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 w-full"
    >
      <div
        class="font-semibold text-sm md:text-base bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xs text-grisPPP"
      >
        <p>
          Our burners regulate <strong class="text-black"
            >100% of the air for combustion</strong
          > without relying on the drum's exhaust system. This ensures total combustion
          and <strong class="text-black">100% fuel utilization</strong>,
          effectively preventing various types of problems.
        </p>
        <ul class="pl-4 pt-4">
          <li class="list-disc">Atmospheric pollution.</li>
          <li class="list-disc">
            Contamination of the asphalt mix with unburned fuel.
          </li>
          <li class="list-disc">
            Clogging in the baghouse and a high risk of fire.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div
        class="font-semibold text-sm md:text-base bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xs text-grisPPP"
      >
        <p>
          <strong class="text-black">Low NOx emissions </strong>(nitrogen
          oxides), a greenhouse gas that is highly regulated in most regions. It
          can be equipped with a flame protection system to reduce NOx to levels
          allowed by the authorities in your region.
        </p>
        <ul class="pl-4 pt-4">
          <li class="list-disc">
            Sealed installation, without cold air inlets, saving the fuel used
            to heat it, allowing for precise and efficient carburation.
          </li>
          <li class="list-disc">
            Efficiency is not affected by changes in weather temperature
            throughout the day.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button
      class="bg-redBg hover:redBgHover max-w-[130px] text-white mt-5 rounded-2xl py-1 px-4"
      aria-label="Learn more about our Heating System">Learn more</button
    >
    <div
      class="w-full bg-[url(/newBanner.png)] bg-no-repeat bg-center bg-cover px-8 lg:px-52 py-20 mt-10"
    >
      <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <img src={flag.src} alt="" class="w-[200px]" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg lg:text-xl">
        Our latest burner innovation features an oxygen sensor that
        automatically regulates excess oxygen to no more than 3%, eliminating
        the need for manual fuel carburization adjustment when relocating the
        equipment. Thanks to our self-carburizing system, NOx levels remain even
        lower.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-[url(/HeroFH.png)] bg-no-repeat bg-center bg-cover">
      <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-10">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-white text-xl md:text-2xl">
          FUEL PREHEATERS
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div
        class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="w-full text-white font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>
            With our preheaters, we reduce fuel viscosity, ensuring proper
            atomization and clean combustion — without delays or the need for
            external heat sources.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-full text-white font-thin text-base md:text-lg flex justify-center items-start gap-10"
        >
          <img src={ficha.src} alt="" class="w-[60px] h-[60px]" />
          <p>
            We raise fuel temperature up to 40 °C, even with flow rates up to
            840 liters per hour.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 py-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 items-center"
      >
        <div class="w-full bg-blueMain p-6 text-white rounded-lg h-[200px]">
          <h2 class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg">
            Problems caused by not preheating low-cost fuels:
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-sm md:text-base">
            <li>Unburned microdroplets cause significant fuel loss.</li>
            <li>
              The hot-mix asphalt becomes contaminated with unburned fuel.
            </li>
            <li>
              This contamination drastically reduces the pavement's lifespan.
            </li>
            <li>
              Additionally, the atmosphere is affected by gases from incomplete
              combustion.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center">
          <img src={preHeat.src} alt="" class="w-1/2" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-bgBeige py-10">
      <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div class="w-full">
          <div class="w-3/5 flex gap-6 justify-center items-center">
            <img src={wordIcon.src} alt="" class="w-[60px] h-[60px]" />
            <h2 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-black">
              Efficient and environmentally responsible
            </h2>
          </div><br />
          <p class="font-thin text-grisT">
            You get lower fuel consumption and cleaner operation, producing
            fewer NOx emissions without compromising performance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full">
          <div class="w-3/5 flex gap-6 justify-center items-center">
            <img src={batchIcon.src} alt="" class="w-[60px] h-[60px]" />
            <h2 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-black">
              Included in every plant, not as a costly add-on
            </h2>
          </div><br />
          <p class="font-thin text-grisT">
            Other brands offer total-air burners and preheaters as expensive
            extras. At Triaso®, we include them as standard equipment in every
            plant configuration — because clean combustion shouldn’t be
            optional.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
